Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 9)
Standards-Version: 3.9.6

Package: caramos-default-settings
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Default settings for CaramOS
 This package provides the default configuration for CaramOS,
 a Linux distribution based on Linux Mint designed for Vietnamese users.
 .
 It includes:
  - Chrome OS style theme settings (dconf/gsettings override)
  - SDDM display manager configuration
  - Default user skeleton (fcitx5, mimeapps, autostart)
  - CaramOS wallpapers and branding
